远远不止于此。 <a href="https://lifehacker.com/keep-a-soap-filled-dish-wand-in-the-shower-for-easy-cle-5927306" target="_blank">在淋浴间放一个，</a>以便在冲洗后冲洗墙壁，这样可以节省<em>将来的</em>时间，因为玻璃和瓷砖不会变得那么脏。</p><p>我 <a href="https://lifehacker.com/home/bissel-crosswave-omniforce-vacuum-prime-day" target="_blank">之前已经提到过这一点</a>，但我的<a href="https://zdcs.link/mVVEv?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Bissell%20CrossWave%20OmniForce&amp;short_url=mVVEv&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>Bissell CrossWave OmniForce</u></a>湿/干真空吸尘器也为我节省了很多时间。它不仅是一个高效的真空吸尘器，而且还可以兼作拖把，这意味着当我想清洁地板时，我不需要花一天中有限的时间在笨重的设备之间切换。您可以单独使用吸尘器，也可以使用双重模式，同时吸尘和拖地，真正节省时间。 </p><div class="pogoClear mb-12 mt-10 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> BISSELL® CrossWave® OmniForce™ 无线多表面硬地板清洁机</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>358.01 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"><span class="text-sm line-through">$379.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $21.98</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/02c7u3U4jaqXfYKWyxQAUCY/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1723658512.jpg" alt="BISSELL® CrossWave® OmniForce™ 多表面硬地板清洁机湿式干式真空吸尘器，具有专用干式真空模式，3882" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/02c7u3U4jaqXfYKWyxQAUCY/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1723658512.jpg" alt="BISSELL® CrossWave® OmniForce™ 多表面硬地板清洁机湿式干式真空吸尘器，具有专用干式真空模式，3882" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>358.01 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"><span class="text-sm line-through">$379.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $21.98</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>常规化学品和产品的增强版也很有帮助，但前提是它们确实有效。例如，我从来没有发现那些声称能够比更便宜的竞争对手更快地破坏油脂和分解食物的更昂贵的洗碗皂更好，但我注意到<a href="https://zdcs.link/2eK8M?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Mr.%20Clean%20Ultra%20Foamy%20Magic%20Eraser&amp;short_url=2eK8M&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">Mr. Clean Ultra Foamy Magic Eraser</a> （2.49美元）磨砂膏比普通三聚氰胺海绵更快地清除浮渣、污垢和粘合剂残留物。同样， <a href="https://zdcs.link/KJMdV?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=PineSol%202x%20Concentrated&amp;short_url=KJMdV&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">PineSol 2x Concentrate</a> （15.82 美元）也比它的标准前身更快地清理了我厨房地板上的混乱。</p><p>虽然到目前为止的产品相当通用，但您还应该考虑那些旨在执行非常具体的任务的产品。例如，清洁微波炉需要花费大量时间，但您可以使用流行的愤怒妈妈设备来减少时间。这是一个愤怒的妈妈的小雕像，你可以在里面装满水和醋，然后用核武器攻击七分钟。它会为您加热微波炉，使污垢松动，然后可以轻松擦掉。 <a href="https://zdcs.link/aX2NJW?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Two%20of%20them%20are%20%2410.99&amp;short_url=aX2NJW&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">其中两件售价 10.99 美元</a>。 <a href="https://zdcs.link/9yXlWP?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Chom%20Chom%20pet%20hair%20roller&amp;short_url=9yXlWP&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">Chom Chom 宠物卷发器</a>（24.99 美元）也将为您节省大量时间。试图手动从室内装潢和地毯上去除毛皮、头发和绒毛是一件愚蠢的事。这使得整个事情的工作变得更快。</p><p>适当的预防也会减少您的清洁时间。例如，我最近非常喜欢我的 SpotLESS 浴室入门套装。这套<a href="https://zdcs.link/Bd70E?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=three-part%20set%20costs%20%2424.99&amp;short_url=Bd70E&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">三件套售价 24.99 美元</a>，包括玻璃和镜子涂层、马桶涂层和固定装置涂层，可防止水斑和其他污垢积聚在平面上。我一直在我的玻璃桌上使用它，并注意到我吃完饭后花更少的时间擦拭表面。其他预防工具，例如<a href="https://zdcs.link/OdVm2?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=floating%20humidifier%20cleaner&amp;short_url=OdVm2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">浮动加湿器清洁剂</a>（6 个，售价 18.99 美元）或<a href="https://zdcs.link/5MxvL?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=ceramic%20sealant&amp;short_url=5MxvL&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">陶瓷密封剂</a>（29.95 美元）（用于台面、不锈钢器具等）也可以防止小混乱变成大混乱，这意味着您不会花费太多钱清洁时与它们打交道的时间几乎相同。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/home/best-tools-to-save-time-cleaning<dc:creator>林赛·埃勒夫森</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Cleaning & Organizing]]></category></item></channel></rss>